00:17:34.420 --> 00:17:35.380
JEREMY POPE: No, I
went into the room.

00:17:35.380 --> 00:17:35.670
TAYLOR FREY: Which
is kind of messed up.

00:17:35.670 --> 00:17:36.830
JEREMY POPE: And
then, he was there.

00:17:36.830 --> 00:17:37.990
