like, lose themselves.

00:32:16.100 --> 00:32:17.240
It's kind of crazy.

00:32:17.240 --> 00:32:18.290
I saw Ted Talk on this.

00:32:18.290 --> 00:32:21.020
And the effects on
the brain of it--

00:32:21.020 --> 00:32:23.600
you actually start to lose
yourself a little bit.

00:32:23.600 --> 00:32:25.640
And you count on
what other people are

00:32:25.640 --> 00:32:28.070
seeing as being the real you.

00:32:28.070 --> 00:32:30.230
And it's insane.

00:32:30.230 --> 00:32:31.880
Excuse me while I
post on Instagram.

00:32:31.880 --> 00:32:33.839
