constant contradictions.

00:33:18.950 --> 00:33:23.420
And so, you're trying to be this
"real artist," quote, unquote.

00:33:23.420 --> 00:33:28.010
And then you have this
element of social media

00:33:28.010 --> 00:33:33.120
that you have to deal with,
which sometimes takes you out

00:33:33.120 --> 00:33:35.220
of your artistic self.

00:33:35.220 --> 00:33:39.030
But it needs to gird or support
what you're doing artistically.

00:33:39.030 --> 00:33:41.430
So there's this
constant give and take

00:33:41.430 --> 00:33:46.920
in flux, generationally
with me, in particular--

00:33:46.920 --> 00:33:51.920
