00:40:13.020 --> 00:40:15.750
it was of everyone, and
everything that he was.

00:40:15.750 --> 00:40:18.120
And that's so rare, even today.

00:40:18.120 --> 00:40:20.520
How did it feel playing a
character where it's like,

00:40:20.520 --> 00:40:24.070
in the '70s, when it's like,
you think of everyone hates

00:40:24.070 --> 00:40:25.520
everyone that's different?

00:40:25.520 --> 00:40:27.030
How was that?

00:40:27.030 --> 00:40:28.800
NANCY TICOTIN: My
experience, personally,

00:40:28.800 --> 00:40:30.672
