a lot of gay guys, always.

00:40:37.440 --> 00:40:40.100
And my parents-- it was
just part of our life.

00:40:40.100 --> 00:40:41.670
There was no question.

00:40:41.670 --> 00:40:44.225
One of my cousins was one
of the dancers in the show,

00:40:44.225 --> 00:40:44.850
in the company.

00:40:44.850 --> 00:40:47.310
